   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="original" xml:lang="en">
            <pb n="1" facs="#s1r"/>
            <head>The Garden of Time</head>
            <l>In gardens where the roses bloom,</l>
            <l>And <del>morning</del> <add>evening</add> shadows softly fall,</l>
            <l>I wander through the <unclear>fragrant</unclear> gloom,</l>
            <l>And hear the blackbird's distant call.</l>
            <lb/>
            <l>The fountain whispers ancient tales,</l>
            <l>Of love and loss beneath the moon,</l>
            <l>While <subst><del>summer</del><add>autumn</add></subst> wind through garden rails,</l>
            <l>Carries <supplied>the</supplied> melody's sweet tune.</l>
            <note>This stanza was revised in 1852</note>
            <lb/>
            <l>Time passes like the flowing stream,</l>
            <l>Through gardens old and ever new,</l>
            <l>Where memories dance and <del instant="true">softly</del> gently gleam,</l>
            <l>In morning's silver-golden dew.</l>
         </div>
      </body>
